query:
SELECT COUNT(*) = 0 as "all_finished: bool"
        FROM polling_station_investigations psi
        JOIN polling_stations ps ON ps.id = psi.polling_station_id
        LEFT JOIN polling_station_results psr ON psr.polling_station_id = psi.polling_station_id
        WHERE ps.committee_session_id = ? 
        AND (psi.corrected_results IS NULL OR (psi.corrected_results = 1 AND psr.polling_station_id IS NULL))
